INSTALLATION UNDER UBUNTU LINUX

# apt-get install liblexical-persistence-perl liblocal-lib-perl libterm-readline-gnu-perl libnet-ssh2-perl libnet-pcap-perl libnet-libdnet-perl libnet-libdnet6-perl

COMMON TO ALL OPERATING SYSTEM

$ mkdir ~/metabrik
$ hg clone -r METABRIK_1_04 http://trac.metabrik.org/hg/core ~/metabrik/core
$ hg clone -r METABRIK_REPOSITORY_1_04 http://trac.metabrik.org/hg/repository ~/metabrik/repository

$ export PATH=$PATH:~/metabrik/core/bin
$ export PERL_RL=Gnu

$ metabrik

Enjoy.

